{"tid":1525024,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"831夜晚9點，我係sogo現場","createTime":"2019-08-31T19:13:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-31T19:56:02.000Z","uid":191338,"like":21,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"8f84f65465e569fb1d334d8f192d247f754b7029","tid":1525024,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:13:25.000Z","msg":"當時防暴8點幾已經推進到軒尼斯道近馬師道位置，十幾部EU同籠車守係果到。<br />\n<br />\n未到9點，已經有部消防車駛左入東角道standby，我同朋友都覺得奇怪，點解冇火燭會有消防係現場。<br />\n<br />\n話口未完，無啦啦，係無啦啦有班人係東角路同軒尼斯道個角位放火，然後幾個消防就揸住個滅火筒整熄左啲火。<br />\n<br />\n轉個頭防暴就幾面同時包抄，我絕對有理由相信，呢個係臥底比防暴大隊嘅signal。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n夜晚11點，旺角站內有設施被「示威者」破壞，防暴衝入站到「驅趕」，轉個頭就去太子無差別恐怖襲擊香港市民。<br />\n<br />\n未到12點，唔夠1個鐘，警務處同政府新聞網都出新聞稿一式一樣。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0LSx6Nf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0LSx6Nf.jpg&h=b36260a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KWFot0B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKWFot0B.jpg&h=899f19a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我絕對有理由相信，呢個係今晚831政府同差佬嘅劇本。同尋晚斬差佬單野異曲同工。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n而家警黑已經全面合作，混入示威群眾內搞事，為左達成佢地嘅目的 - 瓦解示威行動，分化和理非同勇武，令香港市民轉移視線到責難前線身上。<br />\n<br />\n同時，因為香港示威活動缺乏「激進示威者」，所以對家就會cosplay激進示威者混入人群。呢班激進示威者係唔會比人拉/拉左轉頭放，毫無後顧之憂，對香港人嘅示威活動有好大影響。而且要符合止暴制亂嘅條件，林鄭先可以用緊急法，所以佢係10月1日中共大喜之日前一定會將「激進示威者」繼續發揚光大。<br />\n<br />\n-<br />\n<br />\n我建議往後嘅日子，各位手足出黎示威，要有清晰明確嘅目標 target，完成後快閃，唔好逗留，唔好比人拉，唔好被有心人利用群眾利用「示威者」之名黎做新聞。<br />\n<br />\n因為香港政府沒有回應市民五大訴求，仲繼而動武，任由警方襲擊市民，選擇性執法，知法犯法。海外嘅朋友可以幫手發佈「心願清單」，等港共感受下白色恐怖。<br />\n<br />\n完。"},{"pid":"7037aa1e59a22c4dbafb40d39e9e496236d4392d","tid":1525024,"uid":123991,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:13:34.000Z","msg":"我知大家好撚嬲, 因為我地冇清算黨鐵先搞到今日咁, 但係要記得今日要去春袋報仇, 黨鐵黎緊一齊再清算！香港人加油 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Lz7uo3t.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLz7uo3t.jpg&h=4ed7d51c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n九月一號下午一點機場見<br />\n<br />\n901機場和你塞 Channel<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=93cc4dc6\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 公海<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyouopen&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=facc186a\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyouopen</a><br />\n901機場和你塞 宣傳<br />\n<a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyoupromote&d=LDhKEJhCApGKQi337qR8b5zZIytzq3Xhz5Kp58Ixet8%3D&h=0dccf5af\" target=\"_blank\">http://t.me/stuckwithyoupromote</a>"},{"pid":"c6df14b32cfe3a237ed560d74341c1acabcfd2dd","tid":1525024,"uid":28257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:16:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b44b8d7122f8fc96f9576544e8d8b91a8562e09","tid":1525024,"uid":102982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:18:07.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"16cab9b4123addf4220fc8cb0808e36465248e03","tid":1525024,"uid":189652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:18:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eaf97d0ba4cc879eeaaece0580965780cd5cd21f","tid":1525024,"uid":1747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:21:22.000Z","msg":"分析得幾好"},{"pid":"9506eb9616200d5bf906c77e7b7096ea1ea1b6c7","tid":1525024,"uid":21340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:22:56.000Z","msg":"同樓主諗法一樣，分析得好好"},{"pid":"de2298eb9315c117e8556356a6a38209905e1297","tid":1525024,"uid":191338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T19:23:50.000Z","msg":"If we burn, you burn with us <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets